(47, 3, 0, 0, 0, 'Factory Workshop', 'factory-workshop', '<ul class=\"move-ul \"><li style=\"font-size: 0;\"><div class=\"imageContainer ne\" style=\"width:100%;display: inline-block; padding:10px; font-size:14px;vertical-align: top;\">Powerful Magnetic Sweeper is suitable for using in factory workshop, foundry, machinery processing factory, hardware tools factory, large parking lot, construction site ending cleaning and metal recycling station etc. </div></li>\r\n	</ul>', '<ul class=\"move-ul \"><li style=\"font-size: 0;\"><div class=\"imageContainer ne\" style=\"width:100%;display: inline-block; padding:10px; font-size:14px;vertical-align: top;\"><p></p><ul class=\"move-ul \"><li><div class=\"imageContainer ne\" style=\"width:100%;display: inline-block; padding:10px; font-size:14px;vertical-align: top;\">\n<p>\n      <span>\n<b>Powerful Magnetic Sweeper</b><br>\n1.This product is suitable for using in factory workshop, foundry, machinery processing factory, hardware tools factory, large parking lot, construction site ending cleaning and metal recycling station etc. Effectively absorb the small metal pieces, screw &amp; scrap iron which can keep the cleaning of working place and material recycles.<br>\n\n2.The high magnetic force can be kept for a long time and the magnetic sweeper can be used all year round.<br>\n\n3.Simple structure, easy and efficent to use.<br>\n\n4.The magnetic force is focused to the ground and generates a powerful magnetic filed.<br>\n\n5.It has an inside magnetic system. The handle is designed based on human engineering. Through adjusting the handle, we can discharge the material easily and convenient.<br>\n\n</span>\n    </p>\n     \n	</div>\n    \n    </li>\r\n	</ul><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p></div></li>\r\n	<li style=\"font-size: 0;\"><div class=\"imageContainer ne\" style=\"width:100%;display: inline-block; padding:10px; font-size:14px;vertical-align: top;\"><p class=\"pro_det_img\"><img src=\"upfiles/2018327235320282.jpg\"></p>\n<p cl