(376, 'news', 'news_content', 3, '\n                        \n                        \n                        \n                        <ul class=\"move-ul \"><li><div class=\"imageContainer ne\" style=\"width:100%;display: inline-block; padding:10px; font-size:14px;vertical-align: top;\"><div class=\"news_detail\">\n<div class=\"ndet_cont\">\n<p>All the staff of Lishuai Magnetics got on the bus and left for Jiangsu in the lead of Mr. Du at 6:00 am on Sep.17, 2013. Then the unforgettable travel began.</p>\n<p>People all had fun, besides that we had a better understanding how important to get along with each other and the importance of teamwork.</p>\n<p>Travelling helps people relax themselves in nature by going away from city and work for a short time and also help to open our mind.</p>\n<p class=\"pro_det_img\">\n<img src=\"../images/news_detail1.jpg\">\n<span>Mr. Du (second row and the forth from the left) and staff took photo together in Three Kingdoms City</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"pro_det_img\">\n<img src=\"../images/news_detail2.jpg\">\n<span>Taking an oar boat in Jinxi, Kunshan.</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"pro_det_img\">\n<img src=\"../images/news_detail3.jpg\">\n<span>Mr. Du (second row and the tenth from the left), Mr. Lee (second row and the ninth from the left) take the photo with all staff in the Shanghai Branch.</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</div></div><div class=\"mask\" style=\"display: none;\"><a class=\"pull-right remove\" href=\"javascript:void(0);\"><i class=\"fa fa-trash-o\"></i></a><a class=\"pull-right copy\" href=\"javascript:void(0);\"><i class=\"fa fa-clipboard\"></i></a><a class=\"pull-right edit\" data-attr=\"text-block\" href=\"javascript:void(0);\"><i class=\"fa fa-pencil-square-o\"></i></a></div></li></ul>                                                                                '),
