(374, 'page_content', 'pcontents', 37, '\n                        <ul class=\"move-ul \"><li style=\"font-size: 0;\"><div class=\"imageContainer ne\" style=\"width:100%;display: inline-block; padding:10px; font-size:14px;vertical-align: top;\"><p>Have an important question but canâ€™t find it in our quick tips below? then send us an email at <a href=\"mailto:sales@cnlishuai.com\">sales@cnlishuai.com</a> and we will respond to your enquiry within 24hrs.</p>\n    <ul class=\"sup-items\">\n      <li class=\"sup-list\">\n        <h5 class=\"fbd\">\n          <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" viewBox=\"0 0 151 151\">\n            <image xlink:href=\"data:img/png;base64,\"></image>\n          </svg>\n          What Are Lifting Magnets?\n        </h5>\n        <p class=\"flex\">\n          <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" viewBox=\"0 0 144 118\">\n            <image xlink:href=\"data:img/png;base64,\"></image>\n          </svg>\n          The most common lifting magnets are designed to lift heavy metal objects weighing several tons. Other lifting magnets, sometimes called magnetic sweepers, help collect debris like nails, screws, and small metal shards from construction site rubble.\n        </p>\n      </li>\n      <li class=\"sup-list\">\n        <h5 class=\"fbd\">\n          <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" viewBox=\"0 0 151 151\">\n            <image xlink:href=\"data:img/png;base64,\"></image>\n          </svg>\n          How do I place an order?\n        </h5>\n        <p class=\"flex\">\n          <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" viewBox=\"0 0 144 118\">\n            <image xlink:href=\"data:img/png;base64,\"></image>\n          </svg>\n          Lishuai lifting equipment accepts email orders, fax orders and phone orders.\n        </p>\n      </li>\n     