(281, 'news', 'news_content', 1, '\n                        \n                        \n                        \n                        \n                        \n                        \n                        \n                        \n                        \n                        \n                        \n                        \n                        \n                        \n                        \n                        <ul class=\"move-ul \"><li style=\"font-size: 0;\"><div class=\"imageContainer ne\" style=\"width:100%;display: inline-block; padding:10px; font-size:14px;\"><p>With the improvement of the living standards of the contemporary people, some young people with petty bourgeoisie gradually began to enjoy a beautiful viewing experience at home. \n               Here, <strong>CABLETIME</strong> tells you how to choose the HDMI cable that works best for you. Bring a higher level of enjoyment to your movie experience.</p>\n            <div class=\"det-pic flex-sb\">\n                <img src=\"../images/05.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n                <p class=\"cont-txt\">\n                    <span><strong>CABLETIME</strong> Support 8k/60hz 4k/144hz</span> \n                    <span>Premium AL housing for Lux match</span> \n                    <span>Dark Blue-CL3-FT4</span> \n                    <span>high fire-Proof Grade</span> \n                </p>\n            </div>\n            <a href=\"http://115.238.132.142/2019_al/hdmi-cable/\"><span> HDMI Cable</span></a>\n            <div class=\"hdmi-cont\">\n                <p>HDMI cable needs to be long and short The theoretical transmission distance of a single HDMI cable is 10-15 meters, \n                    as long as the balance of 50 cm is enough. If it exceeds 15 meters, <strong>CABLETIME</strong> recommends that customers use amplifiers to amplify the signal. \n                    Generally, 40 meters can be used.</p>\n                <p>Do not choose a cable that is too thin Regardless of the brand, the HDMI cable that is too thin is definitely not available. The material of the core and the \n                    thickness of the shielding layer are all related to the signal quality. The too thin wire must be â€œshrinkedâ€ to the core and the shielding layer, so be sure \n                    to pay more attention.</p>\n                <img src=\"../images/07.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n                <p>Choosing the brand CABLETIME HDMI cable is more worry-free If you feel that your eyesight is difficult to judge the advantages and disadvantages of the HDMI cable, \n                    the easiest way is to choose the brand HDMI cable, of course, the price will be more expensive. <strong>CABLETIME</strong> brand, quality is the best, quality assurance: all wire \n                    quality warranty, use more assured.</p>\n                <p>Pay attention to the interface gold plating brightness Nowadays, the HDMI cable with better quality on the market adopts 24K gold plating, which can effectively \n                    solve the problem of poor contact after the plug is inserted multiple times, so as to avoid the phenomenon of signal loss and affect the picture effect.</p>\n                <img src=\"../images/06.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n            </div></div><div class=\"mask\" style=\"display: none;\"><a class=\"pull-right remove\" href=\"javascript:void(0);\"><i class=\"fa fa-trash-o\"></i></a><a class=\"pull-right copy\" href=\"javascript:void(0);\"><i class=\"fa fa-clipboard\"></i></a><a class=\"pull-right edit\" data-attr=\"text-block\" href=\"javascript:void(0);\"><i class=\"fa fa-pencil-square-o\"></i></a></div></li></ul>                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                '),
