(28, 0, 27, 27, 1, 'About Lishuai', 'Permanent Magnetic Lifter, magnetic lifter,lifting magnets,magnet tools,magnetic tool', 'about-lishuai', 'Permanent Magnetic Lifter Factory, lifting magnets company ,Material handling equipment company,magnet tools factory', 'Zhejiang Lishuai Magnetics Co.,Ltd. is specialized in producing permanent magnetic lifters', 'page_pic1588580352989.jpg', '<ul class=\"move-ul \"><li style=\"font-size: 0;\"><div class=\"imageContainer ne\" style=\"width:100%;display: inline-block; padding:10px; font-size:14px;vertical-align: top;\"><p>Zhejiang Lishuai Magnetics CO.,LTD(original Jinyun Lishuai Lifting Equipment Co.,Ltd. Jinyun Lishuai Sucker Factory) mainly produce: <b>Permanent Magnetic Chuck, Permanent Magnetic lifter, Permanent magnet hoist, Magnetic welding clamps, Electromagnetic Chuck, Heavy-duty electromagnetic chuck, Round electromagnetic chuck, Electric Permanent Magnetic Chuck, Automatic permanent magnet chuck, Automatic permanent magnet lifter, Multifunctional permanent magnet workholding, Turntable permanent magnet workholding, Permanent magnetic chuck, Grids super permanent magnetic chuck</b> and other magnetic products</p>\r\n    <p><a href=\"\">Zhejiang Lishuai Magnetics CO.,LTD.</a>\r\n    (Hereinafter referred to as: Lishuai Magnetics) Founded in 2006 with a registered capital of 5.5 million, it is a professional magnetic application manufacturer integrating production, research and development, and sales. It mainly produces: <b>Electromagnetic Chuck, Electric permanent magnetic chuck, Permanent magnet plane chuck, Permanent magnet hoist, Magnetic welding clamps, Permanent Magnetic Workholding, Magnetic tools and Permanent Magnetic lifter</b> other products. Lishuai Magnetics have a technology research and development team with a solid theoretical foundation, rich practical experience and strong development capabilities. Independent research and development: <b>Electro permanent magnetic pick-up device, Electro permanent magnetic lifter, Automatic permanent magnet chuck, Multifunctional permanent magnet workholding etc.</b> The product won the national invention patent. Through years of cooperation and development with universities, colleges, research institutes and other units, Lishuai Magnetoelectric is at the forefront of the industry in the field of magnetic equipment.</p>\r\n    <p><img src=\"images/about-2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></p>\r\n    <p>In line with the spirit of <b>\"Pragmatism, Dedication, Development and Innovation\" </b>and the business tenet of <b>\"Technology creates quality, integrity creates the future\"</b>, Lishuai people start from the three aspects of \"craftsmanship, equipment, and personnel\" and formulate a A complete quality inspection system and strict control of product quality are well received by new and old customers. In terms of corporate management, we have introduced ISO9001:2008 quality management system standard requirements, strictly implemented industry standards and beyond standards, and established the corporate philosophy of \"being the world\'s top magnetoelectric equipment\".</p>\r\n    \r\n    \r\n    <p>Lishuai Magnetics people deeply feel that the success of the enterprise cannot be separated from the love of users and the enthusiastic support of all sectors of the society. We will work harder, continuously optimize products, and strive to return customers with the best product quality. We wholeheartedly create great achievements and share the future with new and old customers at home and abroad!</p><p></p></div></li>\r\n    <li style=\"font-size: 0;margin-top: -4px;\"><div class=\"imageContainer wd01\" style=\"width: 25%; display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; text-align: center;  padding: 10px;\"><img src=\"http://www.magnetic-lifter.com/upfiles/pic1599616732.jpg\" style=\" display:inline-block;max-width:100%; width: auto; height: auto;\"></div><div class=\"imageContainer wd02\" style=\"width: 25%; display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; text-align: center;  padding: 10px;\"><img src=\"http://www.magnetic-lifter.com/upfiles/pic1599616736.jpg\" style=\" display:inline-block;max-width:100%; width: auto; height: auto;\"></div> <div class=\"imageContainer dw0\" style=\"display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; text-align: center;  padding: 10px; width: 25%;\"><img src=\"http://www.magnetic-lifter.com/upfiles/pic1599616740.jpg\" style=\" display:inline-block;max-width:100%; width: auto; height: auto;\"></div><div class=\"imageContainer dw1\" style=\"display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; text-align: center;  padding: 10px; width: 25%;\"><img src=\"http://www.magnetic-lifter.com/upfiles/pic1599616745.jpg\" style=\" display:inline-block;max-width:100%; width: auto; height: auto;\"></div></li>\r\n    <li style=\"font-size: 0;margin-top: -4px;\"><div class=\"imageContainer wd01\" style=\"width: 25%; display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; text-align: center;  padding: 10px;\"><img src=\"http://www.magnetic-lifter.com/upfiles/pic1599616756.jpg\" style=\" display:inline-block;max-width:100%; width: auto; height: auto;\"></div><div class=\"imageContainer wd02\" style=\"width: 25%; display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; text-align: center;  padding: 10px;\"><img src=\"http://www.magnetic-lifter.com/upfiles/pic1599616760.jpg\" style=\" display:inline-block;max-width:100%; width: auto; height: auto;\"></div> <div class=\"imageContainer dw0\" style=\"display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; text-align: center;  padding: 10px; width: 25%;\"><img src=\"http://www.magnetic-lifter.com/upfiles/pic1599616763.jpg\" style=\" display:inline-block;max-width:100%; width: auto; height: auto;\"></div><div class=\"imageContainer dw0\" style=\"display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; text-align: center;  padding: 10px; width: 25%;\"><i class=\"fa fa-image\"></i></div></li>\r\n    </ul>', ''),
