(282, 81, 'Application', '<ul class=\"move-ul \"><li style=\"font-size: 0;\"><div class=\"imageContainer ne\" style=\"width:100%;display: inline-block; padding:10px; font-size:14px;vertical-align: top;\"><ul class=\"move-ul \"><li style=\"font-size: 0;\"><div class=\"imageContainer ne\" style=\"width:100%;display: inline-block; padding:10px; font-size:14px;vertical-align: top;\">    \n<span>1. Apply to cutting and machining of medium work piece and rough work piece. <br><br>\n2.Apply to small work pieceâ€™s drilling and precision machining.<br><br>\n3. The thickness of the work piece should be more than 10mm.<br><br>\n4. The most appropriate condition of work piece clamping is at least four magnetic pole contact with the working surface.<br><br>\n5. Match the magnetic soft claw and a sliding magnetic block to use, able to solve more function of workpiece clamping processing.<br><br></span>\n<p class=\"pro_det_img\"><img src=\"../upfiles/20142110340743.jpg\"><br><br><br></p><p></p>\n</div></li>\r\n	</ul>  </div></li>\r\n	</ul>'),
